@startuml
autonumber

actor "Player" as Player
participant "Table Games Staff" as Staff
participant "Jackpot System" as System
participant "GEG CRM" as CRM
participant "Customer Service" as CS
participant "GPC Counter" as GPC
participant "Cage" as Cage
participant "Gaming Audit" as Audit

title Progressive Jackpot Process Flow

== Jackpot Trigger ==
Player -> Staff: Progressive Jackpot won
Staff -> System: Verify event & identify player
System -> CRM: Record table number, amount, timestamp

== Record Creation & System Notification ==
CRM -> System: Transmit jackpot event record
CRM -> CRM: Generate transaction record & ID
CRM -> CS: Notify Customer Service team

== Comp Slip Issuance ==
CS -> CRM: Validate jackpot details
CRM -> GPC: Print Comp Slip (unique ID)
note right of GPC
  Duplicate issuance prohibited
  Reprints allowed if not redeemed
end note

== Chip Collection from Cage ==
GPC -> Cage: Present Comp Slip
Cage -> CRM: Confirm validity
Cage -> GPC: Release chips
Cage -> Audit: Log chip release for audit

== Guest Payout at Table ==
GPC -> Staff: Deliver chips
Staff -> Player: Acknowledge receipt

== Redemption Completion & Audit Trail ==
CRM -> System: Cross-reference transaction ID
CRM -> CRM: Update Comp Slip status to "redeemed"
CRM -> Audit: Ret

@enduml